  title="What Is DBT Therapy? Dialectical Behavior Therapy Explained"
  description="DBT (Dialectical Behavior Therapy) teaches skills for emotional regulation, distress tolerance, and relationships. Here's how it works, who it helps, and how it differs from CBT."
